name: BIT.TRIP COMPLETE
overview: BIT.TRIP COMPLETE is a compilation of all 6 award-winning BIT.TRIPgames: BEAT, CORE, VOID, RUNNER, FATE, and FLUX! This COMPLETE version includes a video gallery with more than 25 clips telling the story of CommanderVideo, an image gallery with concept art, and an audio gallery featuring fan remixes, original songs, and demos of BIT.TRIP songs.
